      "content": "\u003cdiv class\u003d\"introduction img-head\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"header\"\u003e\n    \u003cimg src\u003d\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,\u003d\u003d\" alt\u003d\"App Icon\" /\u003e\n    \u003ch3\u003eWelcome to the Lead Generator!\u003c/h3\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \u003csection\u003e\n    \u003ch4\u003eOverview\u003c/h4\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003e\n      Discover, enrich, and score leads using Generative AI models combined with real-time web search via Serper. This system supports both people and company lead discovery with structured outputs ready for CRM integration.\n    \u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003c/section\u003e\n\n  \u003csection\u003e\n    \u003ch4\u003eInput\u003c/h4\u003e\n    \u003cul\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e \u003cstrong\u003eKey Position\u003c/strong\u003e (required): The role or job title to search for (e.g., CFO, VP Marketing).\u003c/li\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e \u003cstrong\u003eCompany Name\u003c/strong\u003e (required): The target company where the person is expected to work.\u003c/li\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e \u003cstrong\u003eIndustry\u003c/strong\u003e (optional): The sector or domain of the company, used to refine results.\u003c/li\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e \u003cstrong\u003eLocation\u003c/strong\u003e (optional): A geographic filter for narrowing down the search (e.g., \"India\").\u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\n  \u003c/section\u003e\n\n  \u003csection\u003e\n    \u003ch4\u003eOutput\u003c/h4\u003e\n    \u003cul\u003e      \n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e \u003cstrong\u003eLead Name:\u003c/strong\u003e Full name of the matched executive or contact person.\u003c/li\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e \u003cstrong\u003eRole:\u003c/strong\u003e The exact job title or designation held at the company.\u003c/li\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e \u003cstrong\u003eCompany:\u003c/strong\u003e The name of the associated organization or business.\u003c/li\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e \u003cstrong\u003eBio:\u003c/strong\u003e A short summary of their background, role, or achievements.\u003c/li\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e \u003cstrong\u003eEnrichment Queries:\u003c/strong\u003e Additional search strings to dig deeper on the lead.\u003c/li\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e \u003cstrong\u003eEmail:\u003c/strong\u003e Official email related to that person.\u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\n  \u003c/section\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n",
